What is Nemiver ?
=================

Nemiver is a standalone graphical C/C++ debugger that integrates
well in the GNOME desktop environment.
It currently features a backend which uses the GNU debugger gdb.

Features
================================
* basic target control (stepping)
* breakpoint management
* debugging session management
* local variables inspection
* call stack management

